quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,53,"Nena, “Oh akapolo anga amene mwalakwira mizimu yanu! Musakayike za chisomo cha Mulungu. Ndithudi Mulungu amakhululukira machimo onse. Ndithudi Iye amakhululukira nthawi zonse ndipo ndiye Mwini chisoni chosatha.”"
  39,54,Lapani kwa Ambuye wanu nthawi ndi nthawi ndipo mudzipereke kwathunthu kwa Iye chilango chisanadze kwa inu chifukwa sipadzakhala wina wothandiza inu
  39,55,Ndipotsatiranizabwinozonsezimenezavumbulutsidwa kwa inu kuchokera kwa Ambuye wanu chilango chake chisanadze kwa inu mwadzidzidzi pamene inu simuli kuchiganizira
  39,56,"Mwina mzimu ungadzanene kuti, “Oh tsoka kwa ine chifukwa chakulephera kwanga pokwaniritsa udindo wanga kwa Mulungu! Ndithudi ine ndidali mmodzi wa iwo amene anali kunyoza.”"
  39,57,"Kapena akhoza kunena kuti, “Akadakhala kuti Mulungu adanditsogolera, ndithudi, ine ndikadakhala m’gulu la anthu angwiro.”"
  39,58,"Kapena pamene aona akhoza kunena chilango kuti, “N’kadakhala ndidali ndi mwayi wina, ndithudi, ndikadakhala m’gulu la iwo ochita zabwino.”"
  39,59,Inde! Ndithudi ulangizi wanga unadza kwa inu koma inu munaukana. Inu munali kunyada ndipo munali m’gulu la anthu osakhulupirira
  39,60,"Ndipo patsiku louka kwa akufa, iwe udzaona nkhope zonse za amene amanamizira Mulungu, zitadetsedwa. Kodi ku Gahena kulibe malo okhalako anthu a mwano"
  39,61,"Ndipo Mulungu adzapereka onse amene amalewa zoipa ku malo awo opambana. Palibe choipa chimene chidzagwa pa iwo, ndipo iwo sadzamva chisoni ayi"
  39,62,"Mulungu ndiye Namalenga wa zinthu zonse, Wosamalira ndiponso Mgawi wa zinthu zonse"
  39,63,"Chake ndi chuma chonse cha kumwamba ndi cha padziko lapansi. Ndipo iwo amene sakhulupirira muchivumbulutso cha Mulungu, amenewo ndiwo amene adzakhala olephera"